<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c4">[١٠٥٥٨]</span> مُغيرَةُ <span class="c2">(١)</span> بنُ حَكيمٍ، أَبو الأَزْهَرِ <span class="c2">(٢)</span> <span class="c2">(٣)</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>أنَّ <span class="c2">(٤)</span> مُعاوِيةَ خَطبَهُم، وعَن مالِكِ <span class="c2">(٥)</span> بنِ هُبيْرةَ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>رَوى <span class="c2">(٦)</span> عَنهُ عَبدُ اللَّهِ بنُ العَلاءِ بنِ زَبرٍ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c4">[١٠٥٥٩]</span> مُغيرَةُ <span class="c2">(٧)</span> بنُ أَبِي رافِعٍ <span class="c2">(٨)</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>موْلى النَّبيِّ -صلى اللَّه عليه وسلم- <span class="c2">(٩)</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>رَوى عَنهُ عَمْرُو بنُ أَبي عَمْرٍو <span class="c2">(١٠)</span> <span class="c2">(١١)</span>.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c4">[١٠٥٦٠]</span> مُغيرَةُ، النَّوفَلِيُّ، القُرشِيُّ <span class="c2">(١٢)</span> <span class="c2">(١٣)</span>.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
